  {
    "id": "m11-ch5-flash",
    "type": "flashcard",
    "title": "Debate Arsenal",
    "description": "Master all the expressions you need to debate with confidence.",
    "props": {
      "cards": [
        {
          "id": "d1",
          "front": "IN MY OPINION,...",
          "back": "In my opinion,...",
          "example": "In my opinion, learning languages opens doors to new cultures."
        },
        {
          "id": "d2",
          "front": "I BELIEVE THAT...",
          "back": "I think that...",
          "example": "I believe that education should be free for everyone."
        },
        {
          "id": "d3",
          "front": "FROM MY PERSPECTIVE,...",
          "back": "Desde mi perspectiva,...",
          "example": "From my perspective, teamwork is essential for success."
        },
        {
          "id": "d4",
          "front": "I'M CONVINCED THAT...",
          "back": "I am convinced that...",
          "example": "I'm convinced that practice makes perfect."
        },
        {
          "id": "d5",
          "front": "AS I SEE IT,...",
          "back": "The way I see it,...",
          "example": "As I see it, we need to focus on renewable energy."
        },
        {
          "id": "d6",
          "front": "I COULDN'T AGREE MORE.",
          "back": "I couldn't agree more.",
          "example": "\"School should start later.\" — \"I couldn't agree more!\""
        },
        {
          "id": "d7",
          "front": "THAT'S A GOOD POINT.",
          "back": "Buen punto.",
          "example": "\"Recycling saves resources.\" — \"That's a good point.\""
        },
        {
          "id": "d8",
          "front": "YOU'RE ABSOLUTELY RIGHT.",
          "back": "You are absolutely right.",
          "example": "\"Exercise is important for mental health.\" — \"You're absolutely right.\""
        },
        {
          "id": "d9",
          "front": "I'M AFRAID I DISAGREE.",
          "back": "I'm afraid I don't agree.",
          "example": "\"Cars should be banned.\" — \"I'm afraid I disagree. People need them.\""
        },
        {
          "id": "d10",
          "front": "I SEE YOUR POINT, BUT...",
          "back": "Entiendo tu punto, pero...",
          "example": "I see your point, but I think there are other solutions."
        },
        {
          "id": "d11",
          "front": "WITH ALL DUE RESPECT,...",
          "back": "With all due respect,...",
          "example": "With all due respect, I think that argument doesn't hold up."
        },
        {
          "id": "d12",
          "front": "HOWEVER,...",
          "back": "However,...",
          "example": "Travel is exciting. However, it can also be stressful."
        },
        {
          "id": "d13",
          "front": "FURTHERMORE,...",
          "back": "Besides,...",
          "example": "Furthermore, studies show that reading improves empathy."
        },
        {
          "id": "d14",
          "front": "ON THE OTHER HAND,...",
          "back": "On the other hand,...",
          "example": "Cars are convenient. On the other hand, they pollute."
        },
        {
          "id": "d15",
          "front": "IN CONCLUSION,...",
          "back": "In conclusion,...",
          "example": "In conclusion, the evidence strongly supports my position."
        },
        {
          "id": "d16",
          "front": "NEVERTHELESS,...",
          "back": "No obstante,...",
          "example": "The plan has risks. Nevertheless, I think we should try it."
        },
        {
          "id": "d17",
          "front": "MOREOVER,...",
          "back": "What's more,...",
          "example": "Moreover, this approach has been proven effective in other countries."
        },
        {
          "id": "d18",
          "front": "ALTHOUGH...",
          "back": "Aunque...",
          "example": "Although some disagree, I believe this is the right choice."
        },
        {
          "id": "d19",
          "front": "OREO STRUCTURE",
          "back": "O = Opinion\nR = Reason\nE = Example\nO = Opinion restated",
          "example": "\"I think pets teach responsibility (O) because caring for an animal requires daily effort (R). For instance, feeding a dog every day... (E) That's why I believe pets are great for kids (O).\""
        },
        {
          "id": "d20",
          "front": "TO SUM UP,...",
          "back": "In summary,...",
          "example": "To sum up, the advantages clearly outweigh the disadvantages."
        }
      ]
    }
  },
